---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-brand-50/30 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-20 md:py-32">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="animate-fade-in">
          <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Perspective â€” Strategic Advisory</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            I help people and teams figure sh*t out and&nbsp;grow.
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
            Building a business can get messy fast; too many ideas, not enough clarity. That's where I come in.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 max-w-lg">
            I'm your Strategic Thinking Partner and problem solver; not the kind who makes decks or reports, but the kind who helps you find clarity and move faster on what matters.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 max-w-lg">
            I work with side-hustlers, operators, and founders of distributed teams (usually under twenty people) to bring outside perspective across brand, strategy, community, and operations.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 max-w-lg">
            If you're feeling stuck or unsure what to tackle next, let's talk! The first call's on me. If I can't help, I'll point you to someone who can.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5"
          >
            Request a Session â†’
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/richard-hero.jpg"
            alt="Richard Kappel"
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-[4/5]"
          />
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-brand-100 rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-16 h-16 bg-brand-50 rounded-xl -z-10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- First Testimonial -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <img src="/testimonial-francesco.jpeg" alt="Francesco Rocca" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover" />
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Francesco Rocca</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Managing Director, Impact Hub Lisbon</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          "Richard's Project Management support, using tools like Trello, Slack, and Google Calendar, transformed our operations at Impact Hub by unifying activities on a single platform and customizing solutions to our needs. His hands-on approach and adaptability were invaluable, fostering a transparent, constructive culture that strengthened team unity. Richard's commitment to understanding both professional and emotional challenges made a significant impact. His guidance and innovative strategies are crucial assets for any organization seeking growth."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Data Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Businesses with Advisors Outperform</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg">
          Firms that receive structured advisory support consistently grow faster, innovate more, and survive longer than peers without advisors.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Global review of peer-reviewed entrepreneurship and SME studies (2000â€“2025).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-brand-50/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Advisory Support Improves Survival</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            U.S. firms that received ongoing counseling from the Small Business Development Centers (SBDCs) showed higher survival and sales growth than comparable non-counseled firms.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-50/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Long-Term Profit &amp; Employment Gains</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            An RCT with 432 Mexican SMEs showed that one year of professional consulting increased returns on assets and total factor productivity, and boosted employment ~50% five years later.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-50/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Mentorship Multiplies Startup Success</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Startups in accelerator programs with structured mentorship raised three times more funding and hired twice as many employees compared with those that only received cash or workspace.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 text-center bg-brand-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold">The Takeaway</p>
        <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-90">
          Across industries and continents, advisors aren't a cost â€” they're a multiplier. The right guidance drives measurable gains in productivity, profitability, growth, and resilience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Tailored Solutions</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg">
          Personalized Support for Solopreneurs, Early-Stage Startups, and Hybrid or Fully-remote Teams.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { title: 'Business Development', desc: 'Strategic insights to refine and enhance your business growth plans.', icon: 'ðŸ“ˆ' },
          { title: 'Project Management', desc: 'External perspective on team dynamics, workflows, and project execution.', icon: 'âš™ï¸' },
          { title: 'Community Development', desc: 'Strategies to build and nurture a vibrant community around your business.', icon: 'ðŸ¤' },
          { title: 'Brand Positioning', desc: 'Fresh ideas to strengthen and evolve your brand in the marketplace.', icon: 'ðŸŽ¯' },
          { title: 'Personal Mentorship', desc: 'Deeply personal guidance to unlock creative solutions and propel you forward.', icon: 'ðŸ§­' },
        ].map((service) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
            <span class="text-3xl">{service.icon}</span>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">{service.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">{service.desc}</p>
            <a href="/advisory" class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 transition-colors">
              Learn More â‡¾
            </a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-16">What People Say</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <img src="/testimonial-lauren.jpeg" alt="Lauren Miller" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover" />
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Lauren Miller</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">makesense Lisbon</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            "Richard brought structure, clarity, and energy to the makesense Lisbon community. He co-created a clear strategy, implemented project management systems, and led in-person sessions that united volunteers around a shared vision. His methods made it easy for everyone to understand their role, stay accountable, and develop real skills in leadership and collaboration. Thanks to his approach, the community became more organized, empowered, and connected â€” even serving as a model for other cities. Richard's ability to combine strategy with human connection is rare. He builds cultures of trust where people feel confident to lead and take action."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <img src="/testimonial-pedro.jpeg" alt="Pedro Coelho" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover" />
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Pedro Coelho</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Founder & CEO, Dumagi</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            "At the beginning of Dumagi's journey, we had the privilege of working with Richard to help us with our brand, and he ended up helping us out with so much more than that. Richard helped us define the direction of our company, structure our digital presence, and build the content that truly reflects who we are today. But his contribution went far beyond strategy, it was deeply human. For me, as founder and CEO, Richard was a true right hand: someone who supported me, believed in the vision, and made me feel that I wasn't walking this path alone. His dedication, insight, and ability to turn ideas into actionable plans made an enormous difference in Dumagi's story."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <img src="/testimonial-camille.png" alt="Camille Bouchard" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover" />
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Camille Bouchard</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Business Owner</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            "I was initially seeking someone to help me organize and structure my business, but working with Richard exceeded all my expectations. He introduced me to the Notion platform, which he custom-designed to fit my specific needs. With Richard's guidance, I was able to effortlessly organize over 10 years of dataâ€”covering collaborators, vendors, clients, projects, and more, allowing me to clear my mind and focus on growth. His expertise has been instrumental in helping me take my business to the next level, including supporting my plans for expansion and hiring new team members. Richard's energy and motivation have given me the confidence and strength to push through the evolution I envisioned for my company."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <img
          src="/richard-about.jpg"
          alt="Richard Kappel"
          class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover aspect-square"
        />
        <div>
          <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">About</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">RichKapp</h2>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              I'm Richard Kappel. At 26, I exited my first company in Chicago. Since then, I've built across industries and continents; launching a hostel, founding a nonprofit that grew into a social enterprise spanning 11 countries with a 40+ person team, and supporting startups from around the world.
            </p>
            <p>
              Through all of it, one thing has been constant: I thrive on solving hard problems and bringing order to chaos.
            </p>
            <p>
              Twenty years in the game taught me one thing: clarity isn't found in books or frameworks. It's built through decisions, mistakes, and the willingness to keep moving when the path isn't clear.
            </p>
            <p>
              Now, I put that experience to work for individuals and teams who want to cut through noise, see what they can't see alone, and move forward with clarity and confidence.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How I Work -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-16">How I Work</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Intro Call</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-600 font-medium mt-1">45 minutes â€” on me</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We'll talk through what's on your plate and what "better" looks like. If I'm not the right fit, I'll point you to someone who is.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Clarity Sprint</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-600 font-medium mt-1">2 sessions in ~14 days</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We go deep on the real blockers and priorities. Top 3 priorities (stack-ranked), 90-day focus with next moves, decision rules & metrics to keep you honest. This is where the fog lifts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Momentum Rhythm</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-600 font-medium mt-1">Ongoing advisory</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Weekly or bi-weekly strategy sessions to keep you moving. Unblock decisions, adjust the plan, and hold the line on focus. No long contracts. I advise; you and your team execute.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 text-lg"
        >
          Request a Session â†’
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom quote -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        My journey has given me a wealth of insights across various disciplines. The services I offer are the ones I'm most passionate about and have honed through experience. By providing a range of services, I can leverage my broad expertise to offer comprehensive, tailored support. Each service empowers clients to tackle their unique challenges and achieve their goals effectively.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
  }
</style>
